I don&#x27;t really buy the &quot;big win&quot; over Sinatra (&quot;much DRYer&quot;, no need to set ivars for each action) because you can just use a `before` block with wildcard routes.<p><pre><code>    before &#x27;/artist/:id*&#x27; do
      @artist = Artist[params[:id]]
    end

    before &#x27;/artist/:id/album/:number*&#x27; do
      @album = @artist.album_with_number(params[:number])
    end</code></pre>
